AUDIO: 'you\'ll understand AI better than most engineers shipping today. So, let\'s count down the real top 10 from 10 to 1 with honest verdicts on each. And stick around because the pattern hiding inside this list is the actual'

[00:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'lesson. First, how I rank these because it matters. I am not ranking by total stars. If I did, boring giants would win every month. I\'m ranking by stars gained this month.'

